  <brief_title>A Comparison of Two Multi-Drug Therapies in HIV-Infected Patients Who Have Never Received Anti-HIV Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of a Four-Drug Regimen Comprised of 141W94, 1592U89, and Combivir With a Three-Drug Regimen Comprised of Nelfinavir and Combivir in Antiretroviral-Naive HIV-Infected Patients.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
